extends layout

block content
  .container.container-clean.pb0.mb20(style='position:relative;')
    .row.mb20
      .col-sm-push-1.col-sm-10.align-center
        h1.mt0.mb10.lato.lato900 #{__('Sign up for exclusive discounts, first dibs on new products and the best new designs')}
        p.m0.lato.lato400 #{__('Follow the best product inspirations from your favorite bloggers')}

    .row.mb15
      .col-sm-12.align-center
        a.btn.btn-danger.btn-lg(href='/signup') Get started
        p.small.mt10
          small <a href="/for-bloggers">Are you Blogger? Find out how we help monetizing your blog</a> &middot; <a href="/sell-products">Sell your products</a>

  .container
    .clearfix.container-fix.p20
      .row.pb20.pt20
        .col-sm-4.align-center
          .clearfix
            i.fa.fa-search.fa-4x.notimp
          h2.mb10 Discover
          p.m0 Build your profile and <u class="lato700">deliver daily products recommendations</u> to your readers. It's easy & free.
        .col-sm-4.align-center
          .clearfix
            i.fa.fa-check.fa-4x.notimp
          h2.mb10 Follow
          p.m0 Increase engagement in your blog, <u class="lato700">give your user one place to find & buy</u> the best products.
        .col-sm-4.align-center
          .clearfix
            i.fa.fa-shopping-cart.fa-4x.notimp
          h2.mb10 Buy
          p.m0 You recommend products and we deliver sponsored links to each of them. <u class="lato700">You earn 70% on every campaign</u>.

  .container.container-clean.pb0.mb20(style='position:relative;')
    .row.mb20
      .col-sm-push-1.col-sm-10.align-center
        h1.mt0.mb10.lato.lato900 The Idea
        p.m0.lato.lato400 Don't ask WHERE TO BUY IT? Just find it here.

  .container.container-fix
    .row
      .col-sm-12
        ul.m0
          li
            h5 Find products recommended by bloggers
            p.m0 Many ad networks deliver random content, often not incontext to your blog.
          li
            h5 Follow your favorite bloggers
            p.m0 Your readers often ask you where to buy products you write in your posts? Out widget is very handy place to deliver this answer.
          li
            h5 Recieve the best deals
            p.m0 We deliver great insights about products you recommend. Now you will learn more witch products are the most popular.
          li
            h5 One place to shop better
            p.m0 We take care on looking for new adverstisers, who will add sponsored links to each of your recommendations.

  .container

    section.mt50
      h3.m0 FAQ
      hr

      h4 I'm blogger. How ShopByBlog works for me?
      p Product Hunt surfaces the best new products, every day. It's a place for product-loving enthusiasts to share and geek out about the latest mobile apps, websites, hardware projects, and tech creations.

      p You can read more about our story on <a href="http://pando.com/2013/12/04/can-the-democratic-power-of-a-platform-like-hacker-news-be-applied-to-products/" target="_blank">PandoDaily</a>, <a href="http://www.fastcolabs.com/3023152/open-company/the-wisdom-of-the-20-minute-startup" target="_blank">Fast Company</a>, <a href="http://techcrunch.com/2014/06/04/product-hunt-is-the-social-news-site-of-tech-products-read-by-influential-people/" target="_blank">TechCrunch</a>, <a href="http://thenextweb.com/insider/2014/06/05/product-hunt-is-leveling-the-playing-field-to-help-good-apps-and-startups-get-attention/" target="_blank">The Next Web</a>, <a href="http://www.businessinsider.com/product-hunt-2014-6" target="_blank">Business Insider</a>, <a href="http://www.foxbusiness.com/on-air/risk-and-reward/index.html#/v/3639940132001" target="_blank">Fox Business</a>, and <a href="http://www.forbes.com/sites/sethporges/2014/07/03/the-creator-of-product-hunt-spills-the-hit-sites-dirty-details" target="_blank">Forbes</a>.</p>

    section
      h4 How much I can earn?
      p You get 60% and we 40% of each deals we'll setup.

      ul
        li URL - Direct link to the product page (avoid links to press or blogs)
        li Product Name
        li Tagline - Very short description of the product (make it catchy!)

